06/11/2006
ANKARA, Turkey -- Army chief General Yasar Buyukanit is describing his recent visit to Greece positively. 
While it may be difficult to settle resolve all bilateral issues immediately, it is vital to keep communication channels open, he said. 
Buyukanit was in Greece from November 1st-4th. 
He met with Greek counterpart Admiral Panagiotis Chinofotis and Defence Minister Evangelos Meymarakis to discuss trust-building measures, regional security and illegal migration. 
(Zaman - 05/11/06; NTV - 03/11/06)
